ỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-H%C3%A0-th%E1%BB%8B-ca-gi%E1%BA%A3/poem-davhlAxUcmWc1D5MHtYkkA">Vịnh Hà thị ca giả - 詠河巿歌者</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/author-ppK7YKfOyDZw9vIHLHbJVA">Phạm Thành Đại</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/V%C5%A9-qu%C3%A1-s%C6%A1n-th%C3%B4n/poem-p0gd829_td00NoHgxK0GSQ">Vũ quá sơn thôn - 雨過山村</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/author-Xw0ALUMVQ06c4vUGFngNbA">Vương Kiến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u/X%C3%BAc-ch%E1%BB%A9c/poem-uWq_FWvkxHkJCbTOrqL5EA">Xúc chức - 促織</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u/author-SkougRiegMs6TZLa1nktmw">Trương Kiều</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/Y%C3%AAn-ca-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2-Bi%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-Kc8R88uruzsjyzzUopw4VQ">Yên ca hành kỳ 2 - Biệt nhật - 燕歌行其二－別日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
